## 目錄結構

```
LF_CSD_NN/
├── README.md / README_EN.md
├── lf_csd_nn/
│   ├── park.py           # Park 變換
│   ├── dct.py            # DCT-II + Hz 映射
│   ├── masks.py          # 柔性頻帶遮罩
│   ├── spectral.py       # LFPR / 熵
│   ├── engine.py         # SpectralEngineB
│   ├── figure_engine.py  # 圖表引擎（Fig 1–4）
│   └── andes_bridge.py   # ANDES + FFT 參考
├── examples/
│   ├── smoke_test.py
│   └── generate_figures.py
├── tests/
│   └── test_engine_b_andes.py
└── LF_CSD_NN.py          # 向後相容
```

---

## 安裝

```powershell
cd C:\Users\User\Downloads\LF_CSD_NN
pip install -e .
pip install -e ".[dev]"   # 含 andes、matplotlib
```

```python
import jax
jax.config.update("jax_enable_x64", True)
```

---

## 快速開始

```python
import jax.numpy as jnp
from lf_csd_nn import EngineBConfig, SpectralEngineB

engine = SpectralEngineB(EngineBConfig(window_size=120, fs=60.0, f_low=2.0))
# t, y = ... ANDES TDS 軌跡
# score_lfpr, score_ent = engine.score_trajectory(t, y, channel_idx=list(range(0, 20)))
```

批次煙霧：

```powershell
python examples/smoke_test.py
```

---

## 測試

```powershell
pip install andes
$env:PYTHONUTF8=1
python tests/test_engine_b_andes.py
```

| 測試 | 內容 |
|------|------|
| TEST 1 | DCT-II 正交性 |
| TEST 2 | LFPR 梯度有限 |
| TEST 3 | 合成信號 DCT vs FFT |
| TEST 4 | ANDES KA 掃描 Spearman(DCT,FFT) > 0.85 |
| TEST 5 | 1000 節點批次 |

